# LAB Objective
To simulate real IT helpdesk troubleshooting scenarios.

## Example Tickets 

### Ticket 001 - Password Reset
User unable to log in due to forgotten password. Reset performed successfully.

### Ticket 002 - Account Lockout
User account locked after failed login attempts. Account unlocked.

### Ticket 003 - Access Denied
User denied access to shared folder. Issue resolved via group assignment.

## Outcome
Simulated real-world IT support scenarios successfully resolved.

